🎯 Objectives
----------------------------------
1)Track overall sales performance
2)Analyze order trends and quantity sold
3)Compare performance across cities and sales channels
4)Identify top-performing products
5)Monitor monthly and yearly sales patterns

📊 Key Features
-------------------
🔹 KPI Cards
1)Total Sales: 31.99M
2)Total Orders: 5044
3)Total Quantity Sold: 13K
4)Average Order Value (AOV): 6.34K

🔹 Visualizations
----------------------
1)Sales by Product
   -Bar chart showing total sales for each product
   -Helps identify top-performing items like Bags, Headphones, Phones
2)Yearly Sales Trend
   -Line chart comparing sales across years (2022–2024)
   -Useful for growth analysis
3)Monthly City Orders
   -Line chart showing order count by month
   -Helps track seasonal demand patterns
4)Sales by Channel
   -Donut chart showing contribution from:
     -Online
     -App
     -Store

🎛️ Filters & Interactivity
-----------------------------------
-Date Range Slicer: Filter data from 2022 to 2024
-City Filter: Select between Hyderabad and Mumbai
-Dynamic visuals update based on user selection
